Sentencas: The effect of water vapor on the mechanical properties of a porous nickel/yttria- stabilized zirconia (Ni-YSZ) composite ( volume ratio of Ni:YSZ = 40: 60) was evaluated at 850 degrees C, a typical operating temperature of a reversible solid oxide cell.
Titulo: Effect of water vapor on static fatigue behavior of a nickel/yttria-stabilized zirconia composite

Sentencas: Both the flexural strength and static fatigue limit of Ni-YSZ obtained from the static fatigue lifetime under a wet atmosphere (containing 4% H2O) were lower than those under a dry atmosphere.
Titulo: Effect of water vapor on static fatigue behavior of a nickel/yttria-stabilized zirconia composite

Sentencas: This can be explained by absorption of H2O molecules into YSZ particles, resulting in accelerated crack growth.
Titulo: Effect of water vapor on static fatigue behavior of a nickel/yttria-stabilized zirconia composite

Sentencas: The fatigue limit of Ni-YSZ was confirmed to be extremely low, corresponding to almost one-third of the flexural strength.
Titulo: Effect of water vapor on static fatigue behavior of a nickel/yttria-stabilized zirconia composite
